The problem is that the value of the dividend is never certain nor is it a bottomless sack.
Last year from ČEZ they allocated 18,000 million to the budget.
Each year of the dividends, ecological damages are liquidated, they serve to complete the income account or serve as a reserve for the prepared income reform.
Furthermore, with this trick, according to EU rules, you increase the true budget deficit to the level of 5.7% of GDP.
The carnival of money transfers does not end here.
Nearly three billion was obtained from the budget to award various compensation to victims of communism and crime, or for litigation expenses, including in construction savings.
It is not clear if the State will need these funds.
It&#39;s a lottery.
If we lose any international litigation, we may have to pay for it, says Janota.
Then the Minister will have to save money within the spring or, in the worst case, dip into the government&#39;s budget reserve.
One hundred million is also missing for the Státní pokladna (State Fund) project, whose price is two billion and which has already been started. It should allow you to monitor online what the different authorities are spending on.
The first stage begins in January.
If the finance minister does not find the money elsewhere, the project will have to be stopped and sanctions will follow, warns Janota.
