Hyundai complied with the unions&#39; requirements. Will cancel all extra work
The management of the car plant in Nošovice agreed with the unions to cancel all additional work.
Precisely because of the frequent additional work, the unions declared a strike emergency on Monday.
The information was confirmed by Petr Vaněk, the spokesman for the Hyundai car factory.
The management, however, wants this year to agree with the unions on one more Saturday shift.
