Last week, my 70-year-old mother was walking through our neighborhood in the municipality of Fuenlabrada when a group of young people between the ages of 15 and 18 passed her and our dog, a mixed-breed, rescued from the kennel. and with no more than six kilos of weight and, without saying a word, they gave him two kicks that left the dog badly injured.
